675
00:59:26,829 --> 00:59:29,195
that doesn't care if Werther dies.

676
00:59:32,068 --> 00:59:34,536
I told them everything.

677
00:59:35,572 --> 00:59:37,267
Naoki was driven into a corner.

678
00:59:37,473 --> 00:59:40,374
The reason he did what he did...

679
00:59:41,010 --> 00:59:42,204
All of it...

680
00:59:44,380 --> 00:59:46,348
was Werther's fault.

681
01:00:10,807 --> 01:00:15,767
Nobody told me that it was wrong to murder.

682
01:00:18,281 --> 01:00:22,581
Rather than picture books and
dream-filled fairy tales,

683
01:00:23,219 --> 01:00:26,052
