708
01:02:08,558 --> 01:02:11,152
All she left for me...

709
01:02:11,360 --> 01:02:14,557
These wonderful books all
had a huge influence on me.

710
01:02:15,565 --> 01:02:17,396
They'll play a big role in your future.

711
